    <entry>
      <title>&#39;Linux-vim的使用&#39;</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/23/Linux-vim%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/23/Linux-vim%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>vim需要安装：yum install vim -y</p><p>配置vim的使用环境，配置文件为 <code>/etc/vimrc</code>，可以在其中增加如显示行号 <code>set nu</code> 或主题颜色 <code>colorscheme zellner</code> 等</p><p>1）插入命令：</p><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">a</span>：在光标后附加内容</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">A：在本行行末附加内容</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">i：在当前光标前插入</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">I：在本行开始插入</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">o</span>：在光标下插入行</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">O：在光标上插入行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2）定位命令：</p><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">:<span class="keyword">set</span> <span class="keyword">nu</span>        设置行号</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">:<span class="keyword">set</span> nonu     取消行号</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">gg            到第一行</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">G                到最后一行</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">nG或:n        到第n行    </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">h，<span class="keyword">j</span>，<span class="keyword">k</span>，<span class="keyword">l</span>         左，下，上，右</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$                移到行尾</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0</span>                移到行首</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3）删除命令</p><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">x</span>            删除单个字符</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">nx        删除后n个字符</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">dd        删除行</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">dG        删除光标所在行到末尾内容</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">D            删除光标所在处到行尾</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">:n1,n2d    删除指定范围的行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4）复制剪切命令</p><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yy，Y        复制当前行</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">nyy，nY        复制当前下n行</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">dd            剪切当前行</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ndd            剪切n行</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">p</span>，<span class="keyword">P</span>            粘贴</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>5）搜索替换</p><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/<span class="built_in">string</span>        搜索指定的字符串</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            :<span class="keyword">set</span> ic    忽略大小写</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">导入文件        :r 文件名</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            :! [命令名]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            :! date</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">查找并替换           :%s/str1/str2/g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 云计算 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Linux </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>&#39;Linux-软、硬链接&#39;</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/23/Linux-%E8%BD%AF%E3%80%81%E7%A1%AC%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/23/Linux-%E8%BD%AF%E3%80%81%E7%A1%AC%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://gitee.com/toki-plus/Figurebed/raw/master/img/rylj01.png"></p><p>硬链接知识小结：</p><ol><li>具有相同Inode节点号的多个文件是互为硬链接文件。</li><li>删除硬链接文件或者删除源文件任意之一，文件实体并未被删除。</li><li>只有删除了源文件及所有对应的硬链接文件，文件实体才会被删除。</li><li>当所有硬链接文件及源文件被删除后，再存放新的数据会占用这个文件的空间，或者磁盘fsck检查的时候，删除的数据也会被系统回收。</li><li>硬链接文件就是文件的另一个入口。</li><li>可以通过给文件设置硬链接文件，来防止重要文件被误删。</li><li>硬链接文件可以用rm命令删除。</li><li>对于静态文件(没有进程正在调用的文件)来说，当对应硬链接数位0(i_link),文件就被删除。i_link的查看方法(ls -l结构的第三列就是)</li></ol><p>软链接知识小结：</p><ol><li>软链接类似windows的快捷方式(可以通过readlink查看其指向)。</li><li>软链接类似一个文本文件，里面存放的是源文件的路径，指向源文件实体。</li><li>删除源文件，软链接文件依然存放，但是无法访问指向的源文件路径内容了。</li><li>失效的时候一般是红字白底闪烁提示。</li><li>软链接和源文件是不同类型的文件，也是不同的文件。inode号也不相同。</li><li>删除软链接文件可以用rm命令。</li></ol><p>目录链接：</p><ol><li>对于目录，不可以创建硬链接，但可以创建软链接</li><li>目录的硬链接不能跨越文件系统</li><li>每个目录下面都有一个硬链接“.”号，和对应上级目录的硬链接“..”。</li><li>在父目录里面创建一个子目录，父目录的链接数增加1(子目录里都有..来指向父目录)。但是在父目录里创建文件，父目录的链接数不会增加。</li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
